data.description: Walk into this charming raised ranch and feel right at home. As you enter the home, you step into a spacious living room with large windows that let in plenty of natural light. There's ample space for seating and entertainment. A cozy fireplace awaits you and those chilly evenings. The open-concept kitchen is equipped with appliances, plenty of cabinet space and a pantry for storage. Adjacent to the kitchen is a dining area, perfect for family meals and entertaining. French doors leads out to the deck, offering an outdoor dining/ entertaining option.The spacious master bedroom includes an en-suite bathroom and enough space for a king-sized bed and additional furniture.The two-car garage is attached to the house and provides convenient parking and storage space. This house is just waiting for your personal touch to make it your home!
